data.description: Very nice 3 bedroom 2 bath, site built home, on 5 acres just minutes from the City of Llano.  This house features over 1900 ft2 of living space with a bonus room, beautiful fire place, huge rock patio, and fantastic views of the distant hills.  There is a very nice workshop with concrete floor, and the water well has been strong even through this drought.    Over the past year the house has taken on an almost complete remodel.  This remodel includes a new AC unit, new roof, new interior and exterior paint, new tape and texturing, new flooring, as well as many other improvements to make the house move in ready.    The property is fenced and cross fenced with abundant wildlife.  It is also great for exploring, a few animals of your own, or simply enjoying the peace and quiet of the countryside.  It is extremely hard to find a small acreage place like this, close to town at an affordable price.
